#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:1
msgid "Configure robots and obstacles"
msgstr "配置机器人与障碍物"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:3
msgid ""
"To effectively simulate robots within your environment, you need to define "
"and configure various robot parameters."
msgstr "要在环境中有效地模拟机器人，需要定义并配置多项机器人参数。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:5
msgid "Robot Configuration Parameters"
msgstr "机器人配置参数"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:7
msgid ""
"Each robot in the simulation is defined by a set of parameters in a YAML "
"configuration file. Below is a simple example of a robot configuration:"
msgstr ""
"仿真中的每个机器人都通过 YAML 配置文件中的参数定义。下面是一个简单示例："

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:9
msgid "The python script and YAML configuration file:"
msgstr "对应的 Python 脚本与 YAML 配置如下："

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:0
msgid "Python Script"
msgstr "Python 脚本"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:0
msgid "YAML Configuration"
msgstr "YAML 配置"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:0
msgid "Demonstration"
msgstr "演示"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:53
msgid "Differential-drive robot moving from its start pose to its goal"
msgstr "差速驱动机器人从初始位姿移动到目标"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:61
#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:183
msgid "Important Parameters Explained"
msgstr "关键参数说明"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:63
msgid ""
"**`kinematics`:** Defines the movement model of the robot. Name options "
"include `'omni'`, `'omni_angular'`, `'diff'`, and `'acker'`."
msgstr ""
"**`kinematics`：** 定义机器人的运动学模型，可选 `'omni'`、`'omni_angular'`、"
"`'diff'`、`'acker'`。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:64
msgid ""
"`'omni'`: Omnidirectional wheels allowing movement in all directions (no "
"orientation control)."
msgstr "`'omni'`：全向轮，可向任意方向移动（无朝向控制）。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:65
msgid ""
"`'omni_angular'`: Omnidirectional with yaw rate control (can translate and "
"rotate independently)."
msgstr "`'omni_angular'`：带偏航角速度控制的全向移动（可独立平移和旋转）。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:66
msgid ""
"`'diff'`: Differential drive allowing movement forward/backward and rotation."
msgstr "`'diff'`：差速驱动，可前后移动并旋转。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:67
msgid "`'acker'`: Ackermann steering, typical for car-like robots."
msgstr "`'acker'`：阿克曼转向，常用于车式机器人。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:69
msgid "**Kinematics Comparison:**"
msgstr "**运动学对比：**"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:53
msgid "Kinematics"
msgstr "运动学"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:53
