msgstr "汽车及车式机器人"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:77
msgid ""
"**`shape`:** Specifies the physical shape and size of the robot. Name "
"options include `'circle'`, `'rectangle'`, `'polygon'`, and `linestring`."
msgstr ""
"**`shape`：** 指定机器人的物理形状与尺寸，可选 `'circle'`、`'rectangle'`、"
"`'polygon'`、`linestring`。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:78
msgid "`circle`: A circular robot with a specified radius."
msgstr "`circle`：给定半径的圆形机器人。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:79
msgid "`rectangle`: A rectangular robot with specified length and width."
msgstr "`rectangle`：具有特定长宽的矩形机器人。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:80
msgid "`polygon`: A polygonal robot."
msgstr "`polygon`：多边形机器人。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:81
msgid "`linestring`: list of lines."
msgstr "`linestring`：由线段组成的形状。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:83
msgid ""
"**`state`:** Defines the initial position and orientation of the robot in "
"the environment."
msgstr "**`state`：** 定义机器人在环境中的初始位置与朝向。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:84
msgid ""
"**`goal`:** Specifies the target position and orientation for the robot."
msgstr "**`goal`：** 指定机器人的目标位置与朝向。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:85
msgid ""
"**`behavior`:** Specifies how the robot generates velocity in `env.step()` "
"when no external command is provided. If omitted, the robot remains static "
"unless a velocity command is passed to `env.step(velocity)`."
msgstr ""
"**`behavior`：** 指定在未提供外部控制指令时，机器人如何在 `env.step()` 中生成"
"速度。若省略该项，除非通过 `env.step(velocity)` 传入速度指令，否则机器人将保"
"持静止。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:86
msgid ""
"**`plot`** (optional): Specifies the visualization settings for the robot. "
"See {py:meth}`~irsim.world.object_base.ObjectBase.plot` for more details."
msgstr ""
"**`plot`**（可选）：设置机器人的可视化样式。参见 {py:meth}"
"`~irsim.world.object_base.ObjectBase.plot`。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:89
msgid ""
"The example above explicitly sets `behavior: {name: 'dash'}` so the robot "
"moves from its initial state toward its goal when `env.step()` is called "
"without an input velocity."
msgstr ""
"上面的示例显式设置了 `behavior: {name: 'dash'}`，因此在调用 `env.step()` 且不"
"传入速度时，机器人会从初始状态向目标移动。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:91
msgid "Explanation"
msgstr "说明"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:93
msgid ""
"**`env.step()`:** Advances the simulation by one time step. You can input "
"your control commands here by `env.step(velocity)` to run your own control "
"algorithm. `velocity` is associated with the `kinematics` of the robot. See "
"{py:meth}`~irsim.env.env_base.EnvBase.step` for more details."
msgstr ""
"**`env.step()`：** 将仿真推进一个时间步。可通过 `env.step(velocity)` 注入控制"
"指令以运行自定义算法，`velocity` 对应机器人 `kinematics`。详情见 {py:meth}"
"`~irsim.env.env_base.EnvBase.step`。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:94
msgid ""
"**`env.render(0.05)`:** Renders the current state of the environment with a "
"0.05-second delay between frames. See {py:meth}"
"`~irsim.env.env_base.EnvBase.render` for more details."
msgstr ""
"**`env.render(0.05)`：** 以 0.05 秒间隔渲染环境状态。详情见 {py:meth}"
"`~irsim.env.env_base.EnvBase.render`。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:95
msgid ""
"**`env.done()`:** Checks whether the simulation conditions to terminate have "
"been met. Such as reaching the goal or a collision. See {py:meth}"
"`~irsim.env.env_base.EnvBase.done` for more details."
msgstr ""
"**`env.done()`：** 检查是否满足终止条件（如达到目标或发生碰撞）。详情见 "
"{py:meth}`~irsim.env.env_base.EnvBase.done`。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:96
msgid ""
"**`env.end()`:** Ensures that the simulation is terminated gracefully, "
"releasing any resources or handles. Provides a clean exit. See {py:meth}"
"`~irsim.env.env_base.EnvBase.end` for more details."
msgstr ""
"**`env.end()`：** 优雅结束仿真并释放资源，确保干净退出。详情见 {py:meth}"
"`~irsim.env.env_base.EnvBase.end`。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:99
msgid ""
"The [rda_planner](https://github.com/hanruihua/RDA-planner) is a case of "
"using the `env.step(velocity)` to run your own control algorithm."
msgstr ""
"[rda_planner](https://github.com/hanruihua/RDA-planner) 展示了如何通过 "
"`env.step(velocity)` 运行自定义控制算法。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:103
msgid ""
"You can add Gaussian noise on the kinematics of the robot and obstacle by "
"setting the `noise` to be True in parameter in the `kinematics` dictionary. "
"See the {doc}`YAML configuration <../yaml_config/configuration>` for more "
"details."
msgstr ""
"在 `kinematics` 字典中将 `noise` 设为 True，即可为机器人或障碍物的运动学添加"
"高斯噪声。详见 {doc}`YAML 配置 <../yaml_config/configuration>`。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:106
msgid "Obstacle Configuration Parameters"
msgstr "障碍物配置参数"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:108
msgid ""
"The parameters of obstacles in the simulation are similar to those of "
"robots. Below is an example of adding various obstacles to the yaml "
"configuration file, and run the same python script as above."
msgstr ""
"仿真中障碍物的参数与机器人类似。下例展示了在 YAML 中添加多类障碍物并复用同一 "
"Python 脚本。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:174
#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:286
msgid "Select Parameters"
msgstr "参数选择"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:185
msgid ""
"**unobstructed**: If `True`, there is no collision detection with the object."
msgstr "**unobstructed**：设为 `True` 时，该对象不参与碰撞检测。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:188
msgid "**Robot vs Obstacle - Key Differences:**"
msgstr "**机器人与障碍物的主要区别：**"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:197
msgid "**Configuration Tips:**"
msgstr "**配置提示：**"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:198
msgid "Objects without `kinematics` are static"
msgstr "未设置 `kinematics` 的对象是静态对象"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:199
msgid "Add `kinematics` + `behavior` to create moving robots or obstacles"
msgstr "同时配置 `kinematics` 与 `behavior` 可创建会移动的机器人或障碍物"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:200
msgid ""
"Pass a velocity to `env.step(velocity)` when using your own controller "
"instead of a configured behavior"
msgstr ""
"使用自定义控制器而不是配置行为时，请向 `env.step(velocity)` 传入速度指令"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:201
msgid "Use `-` to define each new robot/obstacle in the list"
msgstr "列表中使用 `-` 定义每个新的机器人/障碍物"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:205
msgid ""
"Please make sure that the obstacles are not placed in the initial position "
"of the robot. Otherwise, the robot will collide with the obstacles at the "
"beginning of the simulation."
msgstr "请确保障碍物不要放在机器人初始位置，否则仿真开始时就会发生碰撞。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:208
msgid "Advanced Configurations for Multiple Robots and Obstacles"
msgstr "多机器人/障碍物的高级配置"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:210
msgid ""
"To simulate multiple robots and obstacles within the same environment, "
"simply add the `number` and `distribution` of robots and obstacles to the "
"configuration file. Below is an example of a configuration file with "
"multiple robots and obstacles:"
msgstr ""
"若要在同一环境中模拟多个机器人与障碍物，只需在配置中设置它们的 `number` 与 "
"`distribution`。下面是一个包含多个机器人和障碍物的示例："

#: ../../source/usage/configure_robots_obstacles.md:280
msgid ""
"The `distribution` parameter specifies how the robots and obstacles are "
"distributed within the environment. Options include `'manual'` and "
"`'random'`. Details are provided in the {doc}`YAML Configuration <../"
"yaml_config/configuration>`."
msgstr ""
"`distribution` 参数用于控制机器人和障碍物的布局，可选 `'manual'` 或 "
"`'random'`。更多细节见 {doc}`YAML 配置 <../yaml_config/configuration>`。"
